Quantitative Systems Biology 2019 (October 28th and 29th)
Location Programme Speakers Poster


The Monday workshop will consist of a series of talks by invited speakers. There are also poster presentations during lunch and the afternoon coffee break.

Invited speakers:


Becca Asquith (Imperial College London)


Sara-Jane Dunn (Microsoft Research)


Patrick Kemmeren (Princess Máxima Center)


Andela Šarić (University College London)


Dora Tang (MPI-CBG)


Student talks:


Student talks will be held on Tuesday morning. Students wishing to talk will be able to apply in the near future. Please see the QSB twitter, or check this website for information when the applications are open.
